        "TileImage": "$($repository 07923f4a-01d0-46b8-85ec-8cba445dd3a0).Image",
        "Description": "Shihong Luo and Xiaoqing Feng have stolen Chinese state secrets and plan to trade them with a British diplomat for a new life in the UK.\r\rTheir contact, Agnus Pritchard has just arrived in Chongqing. All three plan meet at a local restaurant, where the exchange will take place. You must ensure that these secrets do not fall into Western hands.\r\rIntelligence suggests Luo may still be at work. Feng may be nearby waiting for the signal from Pritchard. All 3 must be eliminated quietly.",
